# Recipe Finder API

## Overview
Recipe Finder is an API that allows users to search for recipes based on available ingredients.

# Recipe Finder API

## Overview
Recipe Finder is an API that allows users to search for recipes based on available ingredients.


Run the app: `uvicorn app.main:app --reload`

## Usage
You can interact with the API by sending GET requests to the following endpoints:
- `/recipes/search`: Search for recipes based on ingredients.

## Deployment
You can deploy the app using Render or AWS. [Include steps here.]

## Technologies
- FastAPI
- PostgreSQL
- SQLAlchemy
- Pydantic
- Uvicorn
